text: St. Joseph, often called St. Joe, is the parish seat of Tensas Parish in northeastern Louisiana, United States. It is in the delta of the Mississippi River. The population was 831 at the 2020 census. The town had an African- American majority of 78.5 percent in 2020. ==References== Category:Towns in Louisiana Category:Parish seats in Louisiana Category:Settlements in Tensas Parish, Louisiana
